    "contentHtml": "<h1>Painting</h1>\n<p>I sometimes paint. Mostly acrilyc.</p>\n<p>Lots of geometry. Geometry is mostly violent; the only shape with no angles is the ellipse. Every other shape has these pointy angles. Even when not pointy, as in an octagon (Or any regular shape with more than 8 sides) it is still an angle and it breaks a line.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/media/painting/00-cover.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1758\" height=\"1758\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>A1 - 100x100</p>\n<p><img src=\"/media/painting/01-screen-shot-2023-04-19-at-23.05.50.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1214\" height=\"1214\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Viajera intergaláctica N1 - 50x50</p>\n<p><img src=\"/media/painting/02-screen-shot-2023-04-19-at-23.05.36.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1426\" height=\"1114\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Viajero Intergaláctico N3 - 30x40</p>\n",
    "excerpt": "I sometimes paint. Mostly acrilyc."
